Privacy Policy

Orthodox Korea App

The Orthodox Korea application respects your privacy. This app does not collect, store, share, or process any personal data from users.
	•	The application is simple and provides access to the official website of the Orthodox Metropolis of Korea and the Exarchate of Japan.
	•	No information is saved on the device or transmitted to third parties.
	•	The app does not use cookies, analytics, advertising, or tracking technologies.
	•	Any data you may provide on the official website (such as contact forms) is handled directly by the website and is outside the scope of this app.

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
Email: leontg@proton.me

